_sText:
<font color="#6666FF">This map was started by archangel505.  He got stuck with it so I pumped some life into it.  he and I continued to work on it for a couple more days, until we got the final product, seen here.

Features:
- 40 Spawns
- Semi-realistic environment
- 2 Special Underwater Areas
- A Zombie Lab

The map isn't all abstract and random like my other maps.  It's got a touch of crazieness but if complication_v6 was too insane for you, this will be your chance to take a breather.  Credit goes to archangel for that lol.  And, many thanks to him overall.  He started off the map, which is always the hardest part.  I just filled in the details.

Questions and Comments are Always Welcome

- Natalya</font>
